('framer',
 'Framer',
 'AI website builder that generates production-ready sites from text prompts',
 'Framer is a visual website builder that uses AI to generate complete, responsive websites from a text description. Unlike traditional page builders, Framer produces genuine code under the hood - React components with proper CSS - which means the output is fast, clean, and extensible by developers who want to customise further. The AI generation workflow starts by describing the type of site needed, after which Framer produces a full layout with sections, typography, and colour scheme that can be edited visually. The component system supports custom interactions and animations without code, while developers can drop into the code layer when needed. Framer also handles hosting, custom domains, and SEO settings in a single platform, making it practical for small businesses and solo creators who want a professional result without hiring a developer. Published sites are genuinely fast - built on a CDN with automatic image optimisation and minimal JavaScript. The free plan supports one project with a Framer subdomain.',
 NULL,
 'https://framer.com',
