 ARRAY['Output requires substantial refinement for final production use', 'Not suitable as a replacement for full design thinking and iteration', 'Less effective for highly custom or brand-specific visual languages'],
 ARRAY['Rapid UI concept generation for client presentations', 'Design direction exploration during discovery phase', 'Fast mockups for user testing sessions']),

('locofy',
 'Locofy.ai',
 'Convert Figma and Adobe XD designs into production-ready frontend code',
 'Locofy.ai bridges the gap between design and development by converting Figma and Adobe XD designs into production frontend code. The AI analyses the design layers, infers component boundaries, and generates React, Vue, Next.js, Gatsby, or HTML/CSS code that matches the visual design. Rather than generic code that requires heavy rework, Locofy identifies design patterns - cards, navigation bars, forms, modals - and maps them to appropriate component structures. The generated code uses proper naming conventions, responsive breakpoints, and handles basic state like button hover effects. Developers typically save 30-60 percent of initial build time on design-to-code handoff, using the generated output as a scaffold rather than writing structure from scratch. Locofy integrates as a Figma plugin, so the conversion happens directly inside the designer''s workflow without exporting files.',
 NULL,
 'https://locofy.ai',
 'https://locofy.ai',
