('uizard',
 'Uizard',
 'AI prototyping tool that turns sketches and screenshots into editable UI designs',
 'Uizard is an AI-powered design and prototyping tool built for speed, not perfection. Its most distinctive feature is the ability to take a hand-drawn sketch - photographed with a phone - and convert it into a digital wireframe with editable components. This makes it useful very early in the design process when ideas are still rough. Uizard also converts screenshots of existing apps into editable designs, which is useful for competitive analysis or when recreating a UI pattern you have seen elsewhere. The AI theme generator produces complete colour and typography systems from a description or a reference image. Uizard is explicitly designed for non-designers: product managers, founders, and startup teams who need to communicate interface ideas clearly without Figma expertise. The drag-and-drop editor uses a library of pre-built UI components that can be assembled quickly into clickable prototypes ready for user testing or stakeholder review.',
 NULL,
 'https://uizard.io',
 'https://uizard.io',
