('visily',
 'Visily',
 'AI wireframing tool for teams to design product interfaces without design skills',
 'Visily is an AI wireframing and design tool that lets product teams create professional-looking interface mockups without a dedicated designer. The AI can generate a full wireframe from a text description, convert a screenshot from any app into an editable design, or suggest layout improvements to an existing mockup. The component library includes over 1,000 pre-built UI elements organised by pattern type - navigation, forms, dashboards, cards - which can be assembled without starting from scratch. Visily is particularly strong in the collaborative features: team members can comment, annotate, and iterate on designs in real time, making it practical for cross-functional teams who need to agree on interface direction before investing in development. The export to Figma feature ensures designers can take ownership of wireframes once the direction is agreed.',
 NULL,
