('relume',
 'Relume',
 'AI website sitemap and wireframe builder that exports directly to Figma and Webflow',
 'Relume is an AI tool that accelerates the early stages of website design: sitemap planning and wireframing. Enter a description of the website - company type, primary goals, target audience - and Relume generates a complete sitemap with recommended pages, then produces wireframes for each page based on its library of best-practice layouts. The wireframes are not generic blocks - they are built from Relume''s component library of 1,000+ website sections that follow conversion-optimised patterns for landing pages, pricing pages, about pages, and more. Everything exports directly to Figma as editable frames or to Webflow as components. For web designers and agencies, Relume eliminates the most time-consuming part of new project setup: the blank-page problem of figuring out site structure and initial layout before doing any real design work.',
