('subframe',
 'Subframe',
 'Visual UI builder that generates clean React code for web applications',
 'Subframe is a visual UI builder specifically designed for building web application interfaces - not marketing pages. It sits between a design tool and a code editor: designers build components visually, and Subframe outputs clean, maintainable React and Tailwind CSS code that developers can integrate directly into their codebase. The component library covers the common patterns of web applications - data tables, forms, navigation sidebars, dashboards, settings pages - and all components are responsive and accessible by default. Unlike tools that generate messy or brittle code, Subframe produces code that follows real development conventions. Teams use it to build internal tools, admin panels, and SaaS product interfaces where visual polish matters but the priority is shipping clean, maintainable code quickly rather than pixel-perfect design files.',
 NULL,
