('penpot',
 'Penpot',
 'Open-source design and prototyping tool built for designers and developers together',
 'Penpot is the leading open-source design and prototyping tool, providing a free, self-hostable alternative to Figma. It runs in the browser and produces SVG-based output that is natively portable - no proprietary formats. Designers work in a familiar interface with frames, components, auto-layout, and a full prototyping mode, while developers inspect designs using a CSS-properties panel that reflects the exact visual properties without interpretation. Penpot is free with no seat limits on the cloud version and can be self-hosted for organisations with data residency requirements. For design teams who moved to Figma from Sketch and are now looking for a privacy-first alternative with no per-seat pricing, Penpot is the most mature option available. The development is community-driven and active, with new features shipping regularly.',
 NULL,
