('magician',
 'Magician',
 'AI magic for Figma - generate icons, images, and copy from text inside your design files',
 'Magician is a Figma plugin that brings generative AI directly into the design canvas. It can generate custom icons from a text description (replacing the time spent searching icon libraries), create placeholder images and illustrations that match a specific style or subject, write UX copy for any text layer, and suggest design alternatives. The icon generation is particularly distinctive - rather than choosing from a fixed library, designers describe what they need and Magician produces a vector icon that matches. This is useful when working on a niche product where standard icon libraries lack the right visual metaphors. Magician works as a single Figma plugin, so it requires no separate subscription dashboard or context switch. It is priced as a simple monthly subscription for individual designers rather than a per-seat enterprise product.',
 NULL,
